  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You attempt to pinpoint a vital part of your patient's anatomy to maximize your healing serums. You can roll a @Check[type:medicine|defense:fortitude] check to deliver a healing serum and compare it to the target's Fortitude DC, even if you target yourself or a willing creature. The target then becomes immune to this feat for 24 hours.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You heal the maximum amount listed for the consumable.</p><p><strong>Success</strong> You heal the target normally.</p><p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The ammunition and consumable are destroyed, and you provide no healing.</p>"
